# FileSystem Example

This is an example of what a FileSystem looks like after it has been Allocated.  This example has a volume data block size of 256 bytes.

## Volume Head Block
Size: 32
```
4B FA 00 01 00 01 00 00 00 00 00 00 08 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 FF FF
```
